WEBVTT

00:00.066 --> 00:01.442
Previously on Ghost Whisperer

00:01.454 --> 00:02.685
The day of the accident,

00:02.723 --> 00:05.014
I saw Jim's ghost step into Sam's body

00:06.454 --> 00:08.240
- You're back.  - Do I know you?

00:08.491 --> 00:10.275
I see the same guy that you see...

00:10.312 --> 00:11.195
It's not Jim.

00:11.214 --> 00:13.503
I just know what I see when I look into those eyes.

00:13.511 --> 00:15.265
And Jim is in there somewhere.

00:15.303 --> 00:16.344
Wait. You're not gonna tell me

00:16.344 --> 00:17.985
you think I'm your husband reincarnated.

00:18.192 --> 00:19.224
I see ghosts.

00:20.234 --> 00:22.800
Because this thing that I do, it's a really big part of me.

00:22.800 --> 00:25.466
And if you don't believe in it, I...

00:25.673 --> 00:27.523
Hey, you needed a little time,you needed a little space.

00:27.643 --> 00:29.072
To get ready to tell me this.

00:29.461 --> 00:30.930
Take all the time you need.

00:36.767 --> 00:38.910
No,no,no. It's easy.

00:39.130 --> 00:41.930
OK? I walk you through it. Do you see the light?

00:43.811 --> 00:44.347
No?

00:45.464 --> 00:46.788
All right, we'll try it again.

00:48.710 --> 00:51.198
OK, great. So you do see the light. OK.

00:51.417 --> 00:53.820
So now just press the start key.

00:53.940 --> 00:55.290
And enter the code.

00:56.518 --> 00:57.382
OK.

00:58.803 --> 01:00.670
Great. All right. I'll see you later, bye.

01:01.434 --> 01:02.871
- Morning.  - Sorry.

01:03.607 --> 01:06.302
Delia is having some trouble with our security system.

01:07.094 --> 01:08.130
That's good.

01:12.087 --> 01:14.387
- You thought that I...  - Into the light,you know?

01:14.760 --> 01:16.570
Well, to be fair,

01:16.570 --> 01:18.380
It looks similar only minus the ear piece.

01:18.500 --> 01:20.305
Do you mind...I really need some coffee now.

01:20.443 --> 01:22.360
No, it's fine. Help yourself.

01:24.252 --> 01:27.343
Look, I know that this is hard to wrap your head around.

01:28.105 --> 01:30.340
But I want to be an open book with you.

01:30.760 --> 01:32.731
Especially with you.

01:33.730 --> 01:34.553
OK,

01:35.069 --> 01:37.530
Well,that's good. Because I've got a lot of questions.

01:37.565 --> 01:39.490
Well, I have some answers.

01:40.320 --> 01:43.037
All right,so this is what it looks like. Right?

01:43.075 --> 01:44.549
When you talk to them.

01:44.886 --> 01:46.816
And how they...wait a minute. First of all.

01:46.816 --> 01:48.746
Are there any of them around here right now?

01:48.992 --> 01:51.311
No. But they do visit me here.

01:51.339 --> 01:53.471
I mean, some because they need my help.

01:53.489 --> 01:55.400
And they know that I have a gift.

01:55.520 --> 01:58.509
And others just pop up when you are least expected.

01:58.910 --> 02:00.050
And you just talk to them.

02:00.210 --> 02:02.740
Yeah, I help them figure out why they still earth-bound,you know.

02:02.930 --> 02:04.251
Get them into light.

02:04.371 --> 02:05.819
Any light does the same thing?

02:06.347 --> 02:07.962
In its own way. Yeah.

02:10.065 --> 02:11.533
A part of the day's work, I guess.

02:11.653 --> 02:12.566
It's not every day.

02:12.686 --> 02:15.972
It's just...when they do show up,I feel like it's my job to help.

02:17.643 --> 02:18.413
Right.

02:19.750 --> 02:20.986
Melinda, I wanna believe you.

02:21.106 --> 02:23.117
A, because I'm crazy about you,

02:23.155 --> 02:26.480
But B because it's just so amazing.

02:29.436 --> 02:31.028
Look, I'm off today, and I just...

02:31.028 --> 02:32.620
I wanna go down and check on the jobsite.

02:32.656 --> 02:35.239
But can I come back and just hang out with you and...

02:36.269 --> 02:38.280
Watch you do what you do?

02:39.767 --> 02:40.970
Bad idea. What's wrong?

02:41.090 --> 02:41.932
No.

02:43.624 --> 02:47.314
No, it's just this is more than...what I do.

02:47.382 --> 02:48.460
It's who I am.

02:48.580 --> 02:51.779
No ghost jokes, I promise. Cross my heart not to die.

